  <title>不愿成为主教的阿塔那修</title>
  <link>http://localhost:65129/posts/%E4%B8%8D%E6%84%BF%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E9%98%BF%E5%A1%94%E9%82%A3%E4%BF%AE/</link>
